  "instructions": [
    "Rinse and shred the canned jackfruit.",
    "Heat coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and grated ginger, cooking for 1 minute.",
    "Add curry paste and turmeric powder, stirring for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Pour in the shredded jackfruit, soy sauce, and a splash of water, coating everything well.",
    "Add coconut cream and bring the mixture to a gentle simmer.",
    "Let the curry simmer for 15 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the jackfruit is tender.",
    "Finish with lime juice, adjust salt to taste, and fold in chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve the curry hot over steamed rice or with flatbread."
  ],
